<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA23">
<l>iḷaippā yiḷaiyāppāy neñcamē coṉṉē</l>
<l>ṉiḷaikka namaṉṟamarkaḷ paṟṟi yiḷaippeyta</l>
<l>nāytantu mōtāma ṟalkuvāṉ nalkāppāṉ</l>
<l>ṟāytantai yevvuyirkkun tāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘You will be weary. Don’t let it weary you, heart’, I said.</l>
<l>When [we] become weary Yama’s people will seize [us and], when we reach fatigue,</l>
<l>they will bring [their] dogs [and] strike [us].</l>
<l>The one who will not let it be granted,</l>
<l>who will grant he is mother [and] father [to us] for all [our] lives.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
